This "new" authordir will not work yet.

All modules using this "system" have a copy of this direcory ($module_dir/jm.evers) included.


If -somewhere this summer- "all" old modules are transformed into the "new authordir" ,
I will adjust the params in scripts/jm.evers/proc/init.proc 


To be precise, in scripts/jm.evers/proc/init.proc

# used for wims read/readproc                                                                                                              
authordir=jm.evers                                                                                                                         
# used for html/apache                                                                                                                     
AUTHORDIR=$module_dir/jm.evers 

should become:

# used for wims read/readproc                                                                                                              
authordir=authors/jm.evers                                                                                                                         
# used for html/apache                                                                                                                     
AUTHORDIR=scripts/authors/jm.evers



